Thursday, July 3rd, 2008

The Police &amp; Military Against The New World Order, an association founded by Jack McLamb, has a singular goal to prevent those in uniform from being unwittingly used to enslave the people of free nations under the anti-God, anti-Freedom (United Nations-led) world government system. The globalists intend to gain, through any available means, total dictatorial control over all the peoples of the world. They cannot realize their goal if their would-be enforcers (police and soldiers) refuse to assist them in their treachery. His motto spells out this truth: 

If police officers and soldiers will not enforce tyranny, it will never be enforced!

Taken from the free GCN podcast, converted to .wav, commercials edited out, re-encoded to .mp3. Editing done using Audacity with labels. One hour duration before commercial edit takes it down to just under 40 minutes of playing time. Genre tag set to Podcast for better ipod compatibility with bookmarking and chapter support. Tags edited, edited picture with Mp3Tag and Winamp.

